        <h1>About Us</h1>

        <p>Welcome to Moffat Bay Resort, where your dream vacation becomes a reality. Located in the heart of the Northwest paradise, our resort offers world-class hospitality and experiences tailored to every guest.</p>

        <div class="aboutus-section">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Moffat Bay Resort was established in 2005 with the vision of creating a tranquil, luxurious, and immersive experience for travelers seeking the ultimate getaway. Our founders, Amy and Craig, fell in love with the natural beauty of this location and decided to create a resort that harmoniously blends with its environment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="aboutus-section">
