            <ul>
                <li>Luxurious oceanfront rooms and suites</li>
                <li>Private villas with breathtaking views</li>
                <li>World-class dining experiences</li>
                <li>Spa and wellness retreats</li>
                <li>Exciting outdoor activities and water sports</li>
                <li>Exclusive event spaces for weddings and corporate retreats</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="aboutus-section">
            <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
            <p>At Moffat Bay Resort, we are committed to providing sustainable, eco-friendly hospitality. We take great pride in preserving the natural beauty around us while ensuring our guests have the best experience possible.</p>
            <p>We actively support local communities through various initiatives and strive to make a positive impact on the environment by implementing green practices throughout our operations.</p>
